data.description: Welcome to your new home! This 4 year old home was designed for comfort & convenience, offering a perfect blend of modern living and classic appeal. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a versatile flex space that can be tailored to your needs; whether it's a home office, a playroom, or a hobby area.  Continue through to find a well-equipped kitchen complete with granite countertops, soft close 42'' cabinets, a large pantry & ample counter space for the aspiring chef. This thoughtfully designed open floorplan provides plenty of space for rest & relaxation. The oversized laundry room is the perfect service area to tackle those household chores & still have room for extra storage. The property boasts an east-facing orientation, allowing you to wake up to the warmth of the morning sun & enjoy beautiful sunrises. The fully fenced backyard provides a private oasis, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying peaceful evenings outdoors. The covered patio is great for entertaining. patio adds to the allure, offering a cozy spot unwinding after a long day.  The garage has an extra flex space as well.  Currently set up as a workout area, but could be used as a workshop or to park toys. This neighborhood has spectacular amenities including a resort style community pool w/waterslide, splash pad, a fitness center, playground, basketball, tennis & pickleball courts.  Additionally, the property is zoned for A+ schools, making it an ideal choice for families seeking top-notch education for their children. Don't miss this opportunity.  Schedule a showing today!
